Edmon Ryan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edmon_Ryan 0 Edmon Ryan (June 5, 1905 — August 4, 1984) was an American theatre, film and television actor. A native of Kentucky, Edmon Ryan Mossbarger was the son of Isham Edward Mossbarger (1864–1936) and Pearl Shelton Mossbarger (1882–1976), He was born in Cecilia and died in Louisville.
